会卖得怎么样，非常退缩，但想到不能一直辜负孩子们的期望，他还是来了到了学校。 孩子们打招呼时，小陈表示内心还是非常激动。第一天在孩子们的捧场下，定价一块一盒的火鸡面，最终入账了 5 、 6 块钱。不过，对他来说，最大的挑战是见到熟人和之前学生的家长。 「昨天就遇到了，也有问，但是我都没有解释。」谈到转行卖火鸡面，小陈坦诚地告诉记者，目前自己仍处于跌跌撞撞的适应期，还会感到尴尬、放不开。 好在妻子很支持他，理解他所做的一切。小陈表示，自己现在还在备考，同时也在自学剪辑，记录着摆摊的趣事。90 后老师失业到校门口卖火鸡面：开始放不开，遇家长会尴尬"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a1b56f33459e7d4010dfad6a2841658b_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "150 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/14911508469"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIy9PW29eQ0Yl6EAMaCTExMzk2Mzk2MCCIkM6+BjAAOHVACHILMTQ5MTE1MDg0Njl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1742390478.577156", "card_id": "Q_604524914", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 139}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么同样是拼反应的游戏，格斗游戏选手到 40 多岁了还能打，而 MOBA 游戏选手却会早早退役？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "格斗游戏例如《拳皇》《街霸》 MOBA 游戏例如《英雄联盟》《DOTA 2》"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-012ee258bfa254e0ad7f631028a14b6a_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "148 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604524914"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy9PW29eQ0Yl6EAMaCDk2NjE5MDk4INGz6KMGMAA4rgFACXIJNjA0NTI0OTE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1742390478.577448", "card_id": "Q_15164822177", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 145}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么爆出蜜雪冰城用隔夜柠檬后，大家不抵触反而更加维护呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这不属于欺骗消费者行为吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-c108d5d2cfc54fe7e97a891c7abdde47_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "145 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": 